  1, 0.925, 0.925],ExpressionUUID->"d92a0017-197e-4c17-925e-76673a496190"],

Cell["\<\
The direct product of kets for different sets of spins may be constructed \
using ProductKet\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.546622479685828*^9, 3.54662252536337*^9}, {
  3.5466228809550943`*^9, 3.546622899159458*^9}, {3.623949114995947*^9, 
  3.623949132012065*^9}},
 Background->RGBColor[
  1, 0.925, 0.925],ExpressionUUID->"0f2d7aa9-eb10-4c66-ad30-19988063ede2"],

Cell["\<\
For example, the product ket of |\[Alpha]> for spin #1 and |\[Beta]> for spin \
#2 may be constructed as follows:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.546622529387289*^9, 3.546622534474881*^9}, {
  3.5466226003573093`*^9, 3.5466226041652737`*^9}, {3.623949136763942*^9, 
