Cell["\<\
Suppose we wish to define the eigenbasis of this Hamiltonian. In general, the \
basis kets of this eigenbasis are generated in no particular order:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7583568236491537`*^9, 
  3.758356858989049*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e8c63d4b-4151-46aa-b1d7-\
