Cell["\<\
The direct product of two bases may be generated using ProductBasis. In the \
example below, the basis is set to the product of the SingletTripletBases for \
the spin pair {1,2} and the ZeemanBasis for spin 3:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.547018354918734*^9, 3.5470183753822536`*^9}, {
