Cell["\<\
An ordering of ZeemanBasis kets which is compatible with the book \
SpinDynamics may be imposed by definining a new basis as follows (the example \
is for a 3-spin-1/2 system, but the code works for any spin system)\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.634196821428035*^9, 3.634196855474257*^9}, {
  3.634196894496873*^9, 
  3.634196911536198*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ed26b448-2487-4bfa-bf76-\
b45fc15d30c0"],

