   "\"the spin system has been set to \\!\\(\\*RowBox[{\\\"{\\\", \
RowBox[{RowBox[{\\\"{\\\", RowBox[{\\\"1\\\", \\\",\\\", \
FractionBox[\\\"1\\\", \\\"2\\\"]}], \\\"}\\\"}], \\\",\\\", \
