Cell["\<\
In the case below, a large chemical shift difference is introduced. \
Secularization leaves only the zz-terms. This is the weak coupling limit.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.630586196884996*^9, 3.63058627925732*^9}, 
   3.630586922146884*^9},
