Cell["\<\
This allows complex symbolic operators to be stored as a numerical matrix \
representation in a defined basis. This can be useful for speeding up \
calculations. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.547483731450963*^9, 3.547483776918331*^9}, {
